### Issue description

See code below.  The `Graphics` object created by `dis->hDC.CreateGraphics()` is not disposed (neither via `DrawItemEventArgs.Dispose()` nor `WmReflectDrawItem()`).  This results in the object having its finalizer run.

https://github.com/dotnet/winforms/blob/9e2fc95fca4e6d18444c819b35bb1338ac6ca63d/src/System.Windows.Forms/src/System/Windows/Forms/Controls/TabControl/TabControl.cs#L1935

```
    private unsafe void WmReflectDrawItem(ref Message m)
    {
        DRAWITEMSTRUCT* dis = (DRAWITEMSTRUCT*)(nint)m.LParamInternal;

        using DrawItemEventArgs e = new(
            dis->hDC.CreateGraphics(),
            Font,
            dis->rcItem,
            (int)dis->itemID,
            (DrawItemState)(int)dis->itemState);

        OnDrawItem(e);

        m.ResultInternal = (LRESULT)1;
    }
```

